name: Compatibilityviewwarning
tagline: Displays a visual warning at the top of a page when a user has 'Compatibility View' mode enabled in Internet Explorer.
body:
compatibilityViewWarning
=====================

Displays a visual warning at the top of a page when a user has 'Compatibility View' mode enabled in Internet Explorer.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
